Reason.Name: Work related ( including property registration etc)
Reason.TermsandConditions:
By clicking on submit, I agree and confirm that

  1. இந்த இ-பாஸ் தவிர்க்க முடியாத பயணத்துக்காக மட்டுமே வழங்கப்படுகிறது. தவறான தகவல்கள் தந்து இ-பாஸ் பெற முயற்சித்தாலோ அல்லது பெற்றாலோ சட்டரீதியான நடவடிக்கை எடுக்கப்படும். / This pass is issued for unavoidable travel only. Providing any incorrect information to get E-Pass will lead to penal action.
  2. All the guest workers must be thermally screened before they board bus or van
  3. On arrival in Tamil Nadu, all the individuals have to be tested using RT-PCR method at the cost of company/manpower agencies. All the individuals who test positive shall be sent to hospital for treatment. All the individuals who test negative shall be sent for ‘room quarantine’ for 14 days at a suitable place identified by the contractor/manpower agencies and approved by the district administration
  4. During 14 days quarantine, if any individual develops symptoms, they must be tested for Covid-19
  5. The TN ePASS will be carried by the applicant and produced for any verification by authorities. A color printed pass copy will be pasted on the windscreen of the vehicle and an electronic copy will be made available to the police personnel at various check posts.
  6. TN ePASS is not transferable.
  7. Misuse of the TN ePASS is liable for prosecution under legal provisions.
  8. None of the passengers have been tested positive for COVID-19 or have come into contact with any Corona positive cases
  9. None of the passengers come from or are going to any of the containment zones
  10. All employees will be under 50 years of age and must not have any symptoms related to Corona and will not have any co-morbidity conditions (such as BP, HT, Diabetes etc).
  11. I have neither obtained any other passes for my organization nor have filled any other application
  12. I agree that any of the passengers shall be subjected to any test as the relevant authorities deem necessary
  13. I also have read the full SOP given in this link and agree to follow it strictly
  14. Any breach of any of the terms will result in strict legal action
